ctions_past_parliamentary2001.html#P 2001 General Election's result]\n\n{{Constituencies of Singapore}}\n\n{{Coord missing|Singapore}}\n\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pasir Ris-Punggol Group Representation Constituency}}\n[[Category:Singaporean electoral divisions]]\n[[Category:Hougang]]\n[[Category:Pasir Ris]]\n[[Category:Paya Lebar]]\n[[Category:Punggol]]\n[[Category:Sengkang]]\n\n\n{{Singapore-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toMichael Palmer(link changed toMichael Palmer (politician)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pasir_Ris%E2%80%93Punggol_Group_Representation_Constituency"}
